r7366 | josef | 2005-08-06 00:17:17 +0200 (Sa, 06 Aug 2005) | 6 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/libggz/m4/ggz.m4

- use 'true' instead of '/bin/true'

Not that it matters much because it should be prefixed with - in a makefile,
but on freebsd there's no /bin/true


------------------------------------------------------------------------
r7286 | josef | 2005-06-18 10:14:03 +0200 (Sa, 18 Jun 2005) | 7 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/libggz/m4/ggz.m4

- new macro: AC_GGZ_VERSION

This can be called as AC_GGZ_VERSION(0, 0, 11).
It will bail out if the version (currently that of libggz) is too old.
Since it needs the headers, it should only be called after AC_GGZ_LIBGGZ.
This macro is very useful for external games.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r7266 | josef | 2005-06-10 13:54:33 +0200 (Fr, 10 Jun 2005) | 3 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
