not helpful for most packages since NLS is manditory.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r6639 | jdorje | 2005-01-13 01:36:29 +0100 (Do, 13 Jan 2005) | 5 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/libggz/configure.ac
   A /trunk/libggz/m4/c99.m4
   M /trunk/libggz/src/conf.c
   M /trunk/libggz/src/support.h

Rewrite make_path.  The new make_path does not use strsep.  It also doesn't
use allocated strings (which were buggy) but instead uses variable-sized
stack arrays.  A configure check is added for variable-sized stack arrays.
The configure check for strsep is removed and a check for strchr is added.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r6638 | jdorje | 2005-01-11 18:36:35 +0100 (Di, 11 Jan 2005) | 3 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/ggz/game_clients/m4/ggz.m4
