------------------------------------------------------------------------
r5838 | jdorje | 2004-02-08 05:34:49 +0100 (So, 08 Feb 2004) | 4 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/libggz/configure.ac
   M /trunk/libggz/src/support.h

Check for strtok and strtok_r functions.  If strsep isn't present and
there's no strtok_r, use strtok as a fallback.  Note that strtok is
probably not threadsafe.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r5837 | jdorje | 2004-02-08 05:30:27 +0100 (So, 08 Feb 2004) | 2 lines
