------------------------------------------------------------------------
r5824 | josef | 2004-02-07 14:37:56 +0100 (Sa, 07 Feb 2004) | 2 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/ggzd/man/ggzdmod.h.3
   M /trunk/libggz/man/ggz.h.3

- doxygen'd manpage update

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r5817 | josef | 2004-02-07 10:48:18 +0100 (Sa, 07 Feb 2004) | 7 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/libggz/src/Makefile.am
   M /trunk/libggz/src/ggz.h

- upgrade libggz library interface number

This was pointed out by Stephen.
It didn't change now, but from 0.0.6 to 0.0.7 new functions were added,
without increasing the 'current' part of the interface version.
To increase compatibility with older GGZs, it is bumped now.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r5792 | josef | 2004-02-05 12:38:16 +0100 (Do, 05 Feb 2004) | 2 lines
