   A /trunk/libggz/man/ggz.h.3

Added man page for libggz.

Unfortunately, the man page does not include the entire documentation.
Since ggz.h defines different Doxygen "groups", these are put into their
own manual pages (list.3, easysock.3, etc.), which are currently not
included (because who would know to look for them?).  A better solution is
needed.

