r4701 | jdorje | 2002-09-25 21:17:21 +0200 (Mi, 25 Sep 2002) | 7 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/libggz/src/conf.c
   M /trunk/libggz/src/ggz.h

Fix a bug in libggz: interface documentation for ggz_conf_read_list was
wrong.

When ggz_conf_read_list is called and no list is present, don't allocate
space for an empty, NULL-terminated list of strings.  Instead just set
the list to NULL.  The interface ducumentation is changed to match.

