r4547 | jdorje | 2002-09-13 18:11:40 +0200 (Fr, 13 Sep 2002) | 2 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/libggz/src/numberlist.c
   M /trunk/libggz/tests/ggzcommon.c

