r4274 | dr_maux | 2002-06-23 21:49:15 +0200 (So, 23 Jun 2002) | 6 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/libggz/src/ggz.h

- when detecting gcc >= 3 is in use, don't use __FUNCTION__, because this is
  incompatible with the latest C standard and will vanish in gcc 3.2 (at least
  the gcc developers say so)
  For gcc 2.95 this macro will still be used.
- remove unnecessary extra path from configure.in

